headline: Extra Space Storage Celebrates 4,000 Stores Milestone
summary: Extra Space Storage, Inc., (NYSE:EXR) the largest operator of self storage properties in the U.S., announced a significant milestone for the company as they celebrate reaching over 4,000 stores nationwide. Extra Space has more than doubled its store count since 2021.
